	<h1 class="title">他一直是世界上最“慷慨”的科学家｜这个人有好奇心</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/37534/small/37534.JPG?1421809836" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">石玉 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-11-08 08:58:57 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/15870/medium/15870.png?1444396965" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


